Module kivakit.kernel
Package com.telenav.kivakit.kernel.language.collections

Interface CompressibleCollection

All Known Implementing Classes:
BaseList, FileList, LinkedObjectList, MessageList, ObjectList, Stack, StringList, ValidationIssues
public interface CompressibleCollection
Interface for collection objects that can be compressed. The compress(Method) method attempts to compress the object using the given CompressibleCollection.Method, returning the actual method used. The compressionMethod() method returns the type of compression that has been used to compress an object. If this value is not CompressibleCollection.Method.NONE then the object is compressed and isCompressed() will return true.
Author:
jonathanl (shibo)
